original_title: 地味巨乳女子大生が童貞彼氏を上回る性欲で絶倫巨乳お姉さんに”性長”した記録。本郷愛
overview: Yuta begins to date Yume, his first girlfriend ever. He is a virgin and she’s an extremely nerdy woman, so it’s only fitting.  But the thing is that after having sex a few times she is becoming more sophisticated, and her sexual desire is growing fast. So much so that it begins to become a problem for him…
title: A record of a simple big-breasted college girl’s “sex length” with her big-breasted sister with a sexual desire that surpasses her virgin boyfriend. Ai Hongo
